							<h1>RESULTS THAT CAN BE MEASURED. CHANGE THAT CAN BE FELT.</h1>
<p>Bloomberg Philanthropies draws on Mike Bloomberg’s decades of experience as a leader in the public and private sectors to deliver real, meaningful, and lasting change around the world. Learn how we’re working to create better, longer lives for the greatest number of people.</p>
